1.title: Prison Break

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: Casting season heats up at Telemundo. Everyone wants a part in the newest telenovela Eva La Trailera, including former Mexican pop singer Raquenel -- whose dark and mysterious past follows her wherever she goes...

2.title: Breaking Brunch

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

2.plot: A celebratory brunch for Raquenel's big new role breaks into chaos when shade & plates are thrown! Things get ugly when Sissi ambushes Raquenel on set. Raquenel opens a box full of dark secrets.

3.title: The Young and Hangry

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

3.plot: A dinner to clear the air between frenemies turns explosive, a scandalous affair is served! Sissi faces off against young and hot competition, Alina Robert. Raquenel goes back to prison!

4.title: Walking Over Red Flames

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

4.plot: An ambush on the red carpet forces Raquenel to strike back! Sissi seduces Gustavo to help her land an English-speaking role. Enrique lures Raquenel to a psychic to uncover her story and a shocking past emerges...

5.title: Blood, Sweat and Revenge

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

5.plot: Jenilca is out for blood when husband Gustavo reveals a sexy text from Sissi. Raquenel plots revenge to take Sissi down. Enrique pushes Raquenel about her past and she baits him with her box of secrets.

6.title: The Devil Wears Revenge

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: Raquenel is rocked by her past when she tries to rebuild her music career. Alina comes for Sissi's role by seducing her leading man! Jenilca and Sissi come to blows. Pepa gets the ultimate Telenovela makeover!

7.title: Don't Call Me a Prostitute

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: A mysterious letter shakes Enrique to his core. Sissi fights for her next role. Raquenel's ladies night out gets crashed and turns into a blowout! Enrique plots to steal a letter from Raquenel's secret box!

8.title: The Starlet Letter

episode of.title: My Life Is a Telenovela (TV Series 2016– )

8.plot: Enrique and Sissi team up to take down Raquenel. Raquenel panics when a letter from her dark past is stolen and chaos breaks loose! Will the letter Raquenel fears the most bury her or finally set her free?

imdb.plot outline: Set in Miami, the show is focused on the real characters who bring life to this enormously popular television genre. The series will follow a group of beautiful and fierce Latina actresses and actors working in this hyper-competitive world. As the series begins, several of our characters are vying for the same role in a real life telenovela being produced by Telemundo, resulting in drama and fireworks on both sides of the camera.
